Package jdbc.query

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomerQueries
    This class contains methods for performing database queries related to customer operations.
    EmployeeQueries
    This class is responsible for executing queries related to employees and guides in the system.
    NotificationQueries
    This class handles database operations related to notifications for orders.
    OccasionalQueries
    Provides methods for querying, inserting, and updating occasional visit orders in the database.
    OrderQueries
    Handles all database operations related to orders, including fetching, inserting, updating, and deleting orders within the park management system.
    ParkQueries
    Handles database operations related to parks within the system.
    QueryControl
    The DB Controller class is the way our application "talk" with the database.
    ReportsQueries
    Manages database operations related to generating and retrieving reports for parks.
    RequestQueries
    Handles database queries related to requests, including fetching, updating, and inserting new requests.
